""" Tests of TrueCallableProxy """
stash = {'call_count': 0}
def wrapped_func():
    stash['call_count'] += 1
    return False
proxy = utils.TrueCallableProxy(wrapped_func)
app = flask.Flask(__name__)
with app.test_request_context('/foo'):
    assert stash['call_count'] == 0
    assert proxy
    assert stash['call_count'] == 0
